Emmerdale star Rebecca Sarker flaunted her behind in a new picture shared with her 35,500 Instagram followers. The 47-year-old was sleeping off the “exhaustion” earlier today after her experience on ITV’s sports game show The Games. The photo showed Rebecca laying face-down on her bed with her perky bottom sticking out of her covers. Rebecca could be seen in the candid shot wearing just a pink tank top and tiny polka-dotted shorts. She captioned the snap: “Out like a light! Bottom line, @thegamestv was an amazing experience. “Highs, lows, exhaustion, exhilaration. Of her experience, the actress concluded: “All's well that ends well. Thank you xx”